<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٤- وَما يَسْتَوِي الْأَعْمى وَالْبَصِيرُ وَالَّذِينَ آمَنُوا وَعَمِلُوا الصَّالِحاتِ وَلَا الْمُسِيءُ قَلِيلًا ما تَتَذَكَّرُونَ <span class="c2">(٥٨)</span> <span class="c2">«١»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٤٥- فَلا أُقْسِمُ بِما تُبْصِرُونَ <span class="c2">(٣٨)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَما لا تُبْصِرُونَ <span class="c2">(٣٩)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>إِنَّهُ لَقَوْلُ رَسُولٍ كَرِيمٍ <span class="c2">(٤٠)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَما هُوَ بِقَوْلِ شاعِرٍ قَلِيلًا ما تُؤْمِنُونَ <span class="c2">(٤١)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَلا بِقَوْلِ كاهِنٍ قَلِيلًا ما تَذَكَّرُونَ <span class="c2">(٤٢)</span> <span class="c2">«٢»</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[تذكر الإنسان يوم القيامة:]</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٤٦- فَإِذا جاءَتِ الطَّامَّةُ الْكُبْرى <span class="c2">(٣٤)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>يَوْمَ يَتَذَكَّرُ الْإِنْسانُ ما سَعى <span class="c2">(٣٥)</span> <span class="c2">«٣»</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٤٧- كَلَّا إِذا دُكَّتِ الْأَرْضُ دَكًّا دَكًّا <span class="c2">(٢١)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَجاءَ رَبُّكَ وَالْمَلَكُ صَفًّا صَفًّا <span class="c2">(٢٢)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَجِيءَ يَوْمَئِذٍ بِجَهَنَّمَ يَوْمَئِذٍ يَتَذَكَّرُ الْإِنْسانُ وَأَنَّى لَهُ الذِّكْرى <span class="c2">(٢٣)</span> <span class="c2">«٤»</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
